 brightening at flare ribbons,\ntherefore contributing to quasi-periodic flare gradual phase emission in EUV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Nov 2022 00:48:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-28"}
