ts at field satisfying a\nmodified energy-momentum dispersion relation within classical regime of general\nrelativity arising as an effective low energy consequence of an underlying\nquantum gravity theory. Our findings may signal new ways of conceiving the\nsubtleties surrounding the physics of dark energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Nov 2022 09:36:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 May 2023 12:01:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-31"}
