ctive to investigate evoked brain rhythms.\nIt may provide a significant refinement to the neuroscientific toolbox for\nstudying evoked oscillations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Nov 2022 10:12:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-28"}
